    {
        "content": "<p>From <a href=\"#narrow/channel/229451-meta.3A-off-topic/topic/Funny.20linguistic.20fact\">Funny linguistic fact</a>, <strong><em>metathetic</em></strong> would be a good term, since it <strong><strong><em>is</em></strong></strong> about a kind of non-symmetric swapping.</p>",
